job description
intel's unmanned aerial vehicles uav organization is looking for an engineer intern passionate about drone robotics and computer vision application
the successful candidate will work closely with product manager other engineer and data scientist to create proof-of-concepts to validate future business opportunity
responsibilities
+ as a drone computer vision engineer you will be responsible for developing and improving existing algorithm for localization mapping and planning
+ you will use your computer vision and sensor fusion technique to merge data from depth camera intel realsense imus and other sensor to make sense of the environment surrounding the drone
+ you will implement the previously described technique and algorithm in intel's state-of-the-art drone technology to demonstrate functionality and feasibility
