inside this business group
perceptual computing perc is an organization within intel tasked with the research development and productization of technology for natural user interaction encompassing both human to machine and human to human experience perc aim to build technology that would help user to have natural immersive and intuitive interaction with computer through not only touch interface but also through hand gesture voice and video the objective of perc is to explore consumer-focused hardware and software application of close-range hand and finger gesture speech recognition face recognition and tracking augmented reality and more
